            Sunderland 'Til I Die: Netflix follows SAFC relegation
            In Netflix's latest documentary, film crews followed the worst season in Sunderland AFC's history.Misery and footballing torture is relived through the series, documenting their Championship relegation season of 2017-18.Made by fans from production company Fulwell 73, Sunderland 'Til I Die is available worldwide from Friday 14 December.
                
                        14 Dec 2018
                    
                
        
